- cs.LG (Machine Learning): Although not directly related to machine learning, the problem of minimizing energy consumption can be seen as a type of optimization problem, which is a common topic in machine learning. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): Similarly to machine learning, the problem of minimizing energy consumption can be seen as a type of optimization problem, which is also a common topic in artificial intelligence.
